ith a - with a load of coal behind him. Father had to chase after him. Oh yes, he would - I remember seeing on the Philog you see there's the old - old hunt - used to be on the heath. The - the Heath House where the collier - where the - well it's - not e
x
actly the hospital but it's on the same land there that - there's the entrance to the hospital is - is the one by the Cross Inn, there was an old road - right of way right there you see, before the houses were built. Well, Heath House. Well they used to c
