ind. But - that's it, well you - you, yes you're right - right clothes you see, that's supposed to keep me dry but it didn't. Oh I told you I've had fun - had fun in the most strange - in that way you see. Well you see the roads were quite safe. I was onl
y a kid, I remember once - a couple of motor cars come about you see, and \{BLANK\}
