cy they were. I had two three of those, I can remember them now, little grey suit, another one was a brown with a - oh and - and - with a blue waistcoat with little round buttons on. I remember counting these buttons like made. I was very - very stuck on 
my clothes then, but I grew up as you know, before I got self-conscious I suppose.
