 no difficulty about it you see, we - when we needed them all right. Oh no, we're not dressed up - very posh you know, no, that was - we used to have patches all right, see. But - I don't remember - see, when I grew up I'm not going to have any patches, s
e
e that business, I had more when I was grown up - in the first - with the war - the second world war, and glad of them. Very funny about that you know. When the war came on we couldn't get coupons you see. It was all right as far as conditions like that. 
