 remember - what it was, I - somebody said something cheeky to me and I - I'm like that see and hit him in the face, back hande}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13060475\charrsid2756420 d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 
 see, not a blow more than that, like that you see, but of course it happened see, and it caught him in the face, up I went of course and that's it. Naturally of course they said, stay up 'til you come down you see, 'til you were - brought down.
