\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Well - I don't - they're both, I mean, like chapel people you see, always behaved properly - and that sort of thing, we had no - that way.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 If you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 A bit slack on that, no, not much celebration. I suppose the
y couldn't afford it, every day was - was a party, was a party you see, not much in the way of parties and that sort of thing. Nothing, no. I do remember when I was up - I was getting about thirteen, fourteen, something like that, my birthday passed over,
 
nobody remembered it. I - I nearly had a tea - supper that - that night, you see, it came out then and they were - old boy handed me a sixpence. But I - I nearly felt like crying that time. You see. No. See, nobody thought of it see. See the trouble my bi
r
thday's too before Christmas. December the fourteenth it was on you see, well of course they're all beginning to think then - Christmas business see. And it had been forgotten completely. So there was nothing much, of course only little - little presents 
round amongst ourselves you see, and that's all but it was not - we were not a - not a family for celebrating things - much you see, no. Never did my family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 You get some families who make a big thing of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Oh yes I know, make a big fuss over li
ttle things like that you see but - not - the same. And of course the time I was coming was the worst possible time. You see, right in the middle of a long family. 'Cos things eased off as we got young - as the younger in the family - the elder sister wen
t off, teaching in Barry and this sort of thing. See things change year by year really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 But you were right in the middle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 I got the hardest time for that you see, and was never any spare money - at that time you see but of course towards the end 
