hese men you know, you know, the working men of those days you see, they were all - you know, just come along for a boss, you know, got a job guv'nor as you were building you see, you'd do that, they'd put on to it what they were, or anything you see. And
 had some very funny experiences with them you see - at times you see 'cos - but he - he got - he could you see. He'd shout at 'em and boss 'em around, he was quite a - you know, in his work.
