e only read one book I think - or was it a play - it was - Mrs Henry Wood I think it was, and he only read this, it was the only books he'd ever read practically or - or - not much that way, until he kind of retired. Then he took to reading you see. But u
p 'til then it was all newspaper. One habit he had - one habit he had was - you know, he said - mother would ask him if he'd read a bit. Oh come and listen to this now, come and listen to this. And she was busy. And she had to come and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 He liked to read out loud?
