 - later, you see. But I never - I - the older ones did for a few years, but I just got - got their names and then they were vague memories you see. So I had no - no - no family, and I remember having to go down to an uncle in Curtaize you see, Uncle Geor
ge he was, and I had to take a wreath. I don't know whether he died or whether the wife - you know, the aunt had died you see, and I just - and I had this address, I'd never been there.
