\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Oh Liberal, Liberal, oh yes, that was the Liberal party, yes, yes, old Campbell Ban
nerman and - and - those in that time so - those are the first politicians I remember you see, Lord Salisbury was the Conservative - Prime Minister, then there was Campbell Bannerman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5532069\charrsid2756420 
bourse}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420  if they voted differently from their employer.
