lais, there see, with - and we were talking, a group of us round there, of course he came up in a dog cart you see, and he was on about yes, they think I'm a - bloody aristocrat, he said, I'm going - haven't got a penny. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 He lived in Tongwynlais didn't he?
