He did - Green Meadow, yes, yes. Yes, yes. Oh yes, that's old Squire Harry Lewis. Or Harry - no, it was Colonel Harry Lewis, the son was Harry Lewis.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 So your father was a member of a political party, if he was an agent he'd have to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Oh yes, yes, oh yes, oh he's keen - oh he was keen politician, in his day, oh yes.
