ections of course, I'm going - I used to have to go round with his - you know, bills - cards used to have printed you see. Vote for Edmond Lewis on them see. Well used to go all over the parish. The population then was about three thousand. Yes, there wer
e
 three thousand - see of these - tickets, used to get up around Birch Grove was included in it, Llanduff North was included in Whitchurch you see, and up into Ton Gwynlais. See, and I used to go and I - and walk - and walk all round all these places with 
these cards.
