Well - see there wasn't so much organisation about - you know, the - it was a simpler life altogether you see. It was just the - the election business, election meetings and that was all you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 What would she do in her spare time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 She never had any. She had no spare - no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Would she have any interests outside the home at all?
