Oh - oh no, no, no, no, no, I don't think - the only time they went - to - together was up to the - first - think it was the Prince of Wales - investiture, but - up at - Carnarvon. YES? WELL he was on the - he was on the distr
ict council you see, and he had a ticket for that you see, and they both went up, and that's about the only time I think - going off like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 That was quite a big do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Oh it was a big affair, because that was something new you see. Yes. See, council}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5532069\charrsid2756420 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 ors and their wives were allowed up there you see, and up they went. That's the only time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 What time did your father get in from work in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Oh well of course always stop work about five o'clock, see, winter 'cos all depends on how far away he was you see. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162986 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
