\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 From the high school}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5532069\charrsid2756420  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
