\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11959078 RL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 Until - 'til the end of that - w
e had to complete the session you see. And there - funny thing, there were two other boys, one from Aberystwyth, the other was from Manchester, doing the same thing, a few of us went over there. Then we joined up then when our year was finished there. I m
ean, we would - you would have had to more or less, some of it was voluntary of course I mean but - couldn't do anything else see. By that time.
