}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7538088\charrsid2756420 ring, there'd be no lectures to attend you see, during the term time, but other times of course with - in the science you got - you got a big exp
eriment on you see and you've got to attend to that, and in your own time in a sense you see.
