 paid him back - and cleared it - almost in that year, but I - I - actually back in the May and in the Army - I was in the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5532069\charrsid2756420  Army when I paid my last insta}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
